{"tid":1050416,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[台灣報導] NHK認證的台灣假新聞「蘇啟城之死」","createTime":"2019-03-07T01:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T02:14:05.000Z","uid":224066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ab959e5c6d5f53f860049d91d22a605a739fd3ed","tid":1050416,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:27:58.000Z","msg":"去年燕子颱風造成日本關西機場關閉，引發大陸外交部派車接人的假新聞，前駐大阪辦事處處長蘇啟誠，也疑似此事輿論壓力太大而輕生。<br />\n這個事件更讓日本NHK電直接點名台灣充斥假新聞！更花了半年時間採訪，報導蘇啟誠之死。<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hui\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hui&h=6788afd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年9月，日本關西機場因為燕子颱風侵襲造成對外聯絡橋損毀，導致上千名旅客受困，當時傳出中國大使館派專車接送中國人，而台灣人只要承認自己是中國人就可以上車的消息，令台灣駐大阪代表處處長遭到國內輿論猛烈抨擊自殺身亡，結果一切經過證實都是造假！<span style=\"color: red;\">NHK昨天播出的特別報導就訪問到當時散播假消息的台灣旅客、台灣網友和台灣名嘴</span>，一起來看看這些人是怎麼看待自己當初的行為&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2huj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2huj&h=753d003b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本NHK電視台的專題報導節目「クローズアップ現代+」在前天(4日)播出去年9月關西機場遭受風災而在台灣掀起的政治風波，<br />\n從節目直接以假新聞(フェイクニュース)為標題就可以看出日本在經過半年的調查以後已經將事件定調為謠言了！<br />\n而謠言的受害者除了台灣政府之外還包括外交官蘇啓誠&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2huk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2huk&h=cd81675e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2013年開始派駐沖繩事務所<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hul\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hul&h=50565fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2018年7月轉至大阪事務所<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2huM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2huM&h=48d897bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n節目先介紹了蘇啓誠外交官的資歷，而在他2018年7月派往大阪之後的兩個月就發生憾事<br />\n2018年9月4日，關西機場成了孤島！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2huN\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2huN&h=5a6d3852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n建於海上的關西機場在2018年9月4日因為燕子颱風侵襲導致聯外橋樑毀損封閉，航班又不能正常起降，於是所有旅客就被困在機場進退不得！大約有3000名旅客被困在關西機場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2huO\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2huO&h=e2d15f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其中3分之1是外國人<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2huP\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2huP&h=eaab18fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隔天9月5日早上，旅客們終於盼到一線曙光！<br />\n接駁巴士陸續抵達接送旅客離開機場！<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2huq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2huq&h=f225d0a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hur\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hur&h=e0907f4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這些接駁巴士都是由關西機場安排的，然而這個時候中國的社群網站微博卻傳出一個消息，一篇微博瘋傳稱讚中國的文章！<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hus\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hus&h=582c182e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2huT\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2huT&h=65c98fa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「我們（中國）的大使館第一時間協調機場安排專車」<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2huU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2huU&h=dd75e8cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「台灣人承認自己是中國人就可以上車跟祖國走」<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2huV\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2huV&h=cfc04722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「強大的中國力量讚讚讚」<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2huW\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2huW&h=777c2047&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這個消息傳到受困旅客的台灣旅客耳裡&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n當時受困機場的一對汪姓母女表示，<br />\n她們也從中國旅客口中聽到這個消息，隨後沒查證就轉發「中國大使館派車來接」這個消息。<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hux\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hux&h=8f2d9f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2huZ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2huZ&h=8516f89a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女兒說自己雖然懷疑但還是上車了，<br />\n「我雖然懷疑為什麼只有中國派車來，但只想早點回家所以也不多想了」<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hva\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hva&h=e59cfdea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她們母女的文章加上其他旅客的傳言陸續傳回台灣以後，網友和名嘴們都開始砲轟抨擊駐日代表處。<br />\nPTT網友更群起砲轟。<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hvC\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hvC&h=efa79a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hvD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hvD&h=7270a2e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNHK電視台竟然可以訪問到一位當時罵駐日代表處的網友<br />\n「當時看到有7、8位朋友都在傳這個消息，我就以為是真的了」<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hve\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hve&h=6afe6abd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hvf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hvf&h=784bc553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">節目還指出政論節目（關鍵時刻）和在野黨（國民黨）不放過這個機會窮追猛打！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hvg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hvg&h=c0f7a236&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hvh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hvh&h=9894b260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n名嘴黃暐瀚也接受NHK訪問，他說新聞就是要搶快，沒時間辨識真假<br />\n「電視、新聞慢了半天或一天報導，收視率就會降很多」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hvI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hvI&h=801a7a3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「不能比網路還慢因此沒有確認事實」<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hvJ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hvJ&h=92afd5d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘇啓誠外交官一邊替旅客安排車票和住宿，一邊還得應付無止盡的抗議，承受不住壓力在9月14日自殺身亡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hvK\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hvK&h=2a13b2b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朋友轉述他當時「怎麼解釋都沒人聽」的無奈<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hvL\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hvL&h=b7c48a09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來經過查證確定巴士都是關西機場安排的，跟中國大使館一點關係都沒有，那麼散播假新聞的旅客、網友和名嘴有什麼看法呢？<br />\n<br />\n先是這對散播「中國大使館幫忙」的母女<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hvm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hvm&h=af4a4252&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「沒想到那個情報竟然是假的&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hvn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hvn&h=bdffedbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「我沒辦法分辨消息究竟是真是假」<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hvo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hvo&h=05438ad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n名嘴黃暐瀚則是透過網路道歉，並表示<br />\n「消息傳播的速度很快很難驗證，但也只能想辦法驗證，我已經深刻反省了」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hvp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hvp&h=0d39cd10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hvQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hvQ&h=15b7054b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.cc/image/aaaaa2hvR\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.cc%2Fimage%2Faaaaa2hvR&h=0702aaa5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21a767a0bf43ef9db0a32e50592f14db91a85670","tid":1050416,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T01:28:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O99RuNDmGWc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DO99RuNDmGWc&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QKg2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=034ea217\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O99RuNDmGWc</a>"},{"pid":"8be707ef4a6177b1c1f602ee48830a2e3597269d","tid":1050416,"uid":60585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:14:05.000Z","msg":"中國製造、英國研究、韓國起源、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">台灣報導</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}